{"tid":803629,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[理性研究] 從香港住戶數目 、樓盤未來之供求量估計未來樓價走勢","createTime":"2018-09-02T12:08:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T13:14:34.000Z","uid":204131,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6c970df1eaf1542f1b0506fbd5334ff3903db85f","tid":803629,"uid":204131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T12:08:52.000Z","msg":"香港人口推算2017-2066顯示 住戶數目將會由二零一六年的251萬(每個家庭住戶大約係2.7人)，逐步增長至二零四六年297萬的頂峰，三十年間整體增加了46萬住戶，之後緩慢下跌至二零五一年的295萬住戶(人口老化關係)。 <br />\n根據房屋統計數字2017 <br />\n公營及私人永久性房屋的單位數目大約有270萬個 <br />\n而係呢三十年 每年大約有2萬個住戶(需求)增加 <br />\n而政府亦開始正視樓價問題 公營/資助房屋興建數量 由過往每年13000左右 <br />\n到而家每年30000，加上私營房屋每年 10000左右 預計5年後落成數量每年大約有40,000伙(重有上升趨勢) <br />\n<br />\n業主只會愈來愈賣唔出 而家重有空置稅 ，發展商而家囤積個10萬伙單位到時逼住放 到時樓價真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且30年後人口老化+ 死左的人騰空單位 2047回歸不穩定因素 樓價下跌更加唔洗諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://images.edigest.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/1875a_acsa28_box_203925693259db5295b2311.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.edigest.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2F1875a_acsa28_box_203925693259db5295b2311.png&h=77e357a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7bbb00c282bd91fa2ef34523858d1bc21f14bd75","tid":803629,"uid":9231,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T12:12:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/02/201235_5a779013ee58ff7a3dcfdce0a24df9f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F02%2F201235_5a779013ee58ff7a3dcfdce0a24df9f7.jpg&h=40dcb53d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fec3887068b647c516481451ccaa38967fb47f7d","tid":803629,"uid":190540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T12:12:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e9233e9ed9c6ec018ff8bbf2bb299ba1bc8928c","tid":803629,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bbb00c282b